						               													<description>Mutant Chronicles: Warzone Resurrection is a tabletop wargame set in the dystopian future of the Mutant Chronicles Universe.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;With five Mega corporations at war with each other, each on trying to control as much of the the solar system as they can, a much larger threat has appeared from the darkness of the void. The mutated and terrifying hordes of the Dark Legion threaten to over whelm humanity and only the light of the Cardinal and The Brotherhood can unite the factions, to stand against this tide of evil.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;Based on the Wargame Adaptive Ruleset (WAR), Mutant Chronicles: Warzone Resurrection is a fast-paced, tactical game that pits the forces of two or more players against each other. Mutant Chronicles: Warzone Resurrection can be played from small skirmish fights of a squad or two, to large scale battles. Iconic heroes from the Mutant Chronicles universe lead their forces to victory!&amp;#10;&amp;#10;460+ pages or full color rules and background material on each unit.&amp;#10;Tournament-ready missions&amp;#10;Escalation rules for leagues or campaigns&amp;#10;9 Full factions including heroes and vehicles.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;This edition adds two army lists as well as league rules. Miniatures stay the same, but stat lines updated. Each army list now has its own advanced combat cards deck; those cards combined into one deck with two entries on each card, some generic, some faction specific.&amp;#10;&amp;#10;</description>
